SUMMARY:God save the Queen!
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Join Queen Elizabeth II in God Save the Queen! — a no-holds-b
 arred\, warts-and-all one-woman comedy spectacular where Her Maj finally sp
 ills the royal tea. From awkward palace dinners and eyebrow-raising prime m
 inisters to scandalous royal rivalries and the secrets behind the crown\, n
 othing is off-limits as Lizzy tells her side of the story with razor-sharp 
 wit\, biting charm\, and a gin firmly in hand. Expect scandal\, sass\, and 
 revelations you definitely won’t hear at the palace gates — all deliver
 ed with camp flair and regal confidence. The Queen is fabulously portrayed 
 by Lady Red Velvet\, British drag artist living in Barcelona and a powerhou
 se international entertainer. An award-winning LGBTQ+ activist\, Lady Red V
 elvet is also the creator of the cult hit Dragatha Christie\, blending drag
 \, theatre\, and murder mystery into unforgettable stage experiences. Known
  for sharp improvisation\, commanding stage presence\, and quick-fire comed
 y\, she brings both reverence and irreverence to the role\nMore info: https
 ://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/god-save-the-queen/
